      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KAREN STRATUS (5) has a strong record this track and trip including two wins from three starts. Hit the frame latest (15.94) when second at The Gardens in a Grade 4/5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. MRS. JACOBS (2) showed strong early pace from the wide draw and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fourth over 300m this track in 17.73. Expected to give a good account. TRICKLE (1) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (23.29) at The Gardens in a Grade 3/4. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. AUSSIE OSCAR (3) deserves plenty of thought over this trip. Something for the Multiples: KARLI MULWEE (6)",
